{"tid":2166301,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"應承我，唔好再眾籌送錢畀腐敗嘅制度","createTime":"2020-08-20T10:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T13:03:45.000Z","uid":207710,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2a7b07669a83e305e43a1b97536f53dd2c1610f7","tid":2166301,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:32:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200818/OH4ICE4J3NENVIOTZISCDYO35Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200818%2FOH4ICE4J3NENVIOTZISCDYO35Q%2F&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5V8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=42aeba56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200818%2FOH4ICE4J3NENVIOTZISCDYO35Q%2F&h=2aca9565\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200818/OH4ICE4J3NENVIOTZISCDYO35Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n明白大家都對呢個司法制度好憤慨<br />\n亦都唔反對被政府告嘅抗爭者抗辯或者打官司<br />\n畢竟坐少一年得一年<br />\n<br />\n但主動去眾籌使錢經法院去告政府/司法覆核已經唔work咗好耐<br />\n三權分立已經唔存在咗好耐<br />\n亦都唔需要再使有限嘅資源去「證明香港無法治」<br />\n可以用喺國際線/感化藍絲去證明無法治嘅案例已經夠晒<br />\n之後再使錢喺呢方面嘅邊際效益只會遞減<br />\n<br />\n希望大家慳返筆錢，唔好送錢畀紅底律政/法官/政府<br />\n要搞司法覆核都要用法援之類<br />\n攞唔到就唔好搞<br />\n慳返筆錢用喺其他幫到抗爭嘅途徑<br />\n今次呢三百萬，就當最後一次嘅「證明香港無法治」開支"},{"pid":"0ba8cac504e9a4e864862f30488c0dbabc7b7f46","tid":2166301,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:35:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ece14fcc7cfbffee8fed18051012b5c083bf9f75","tid":2166301,"uid":247211,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a7b07669a83e305e43a1b97536f53dd2c1610f7","tid":2166301,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:32:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200818/OH4ICE4J3NENVIOTZISCDYO35Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200818%2FOH4ICE4J3NENVIOTZISCDYO35Q%2F&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5V8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=42aeba56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=h